Enum ApprovalRoleCode

    public enum ApprovalRoleCode
extends java.lang.Enum<ApprovalRoleCode>
    Discount Approval Request (DAR) approval role codes. NOTE that the order of these codes matters! A role's position in this declaration determines its approval rank!
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
